ZH: 我把这个任务留给了我的同事。
EN: I left this task to my colleague.

ZH: 请将座位留给那位老人。
EN: Please leave the seat for the elderly person.

ZH: 我们留给了足够的时间来准备这个项目。
EN: We left enough time to prepare for this project.

ZH: 把一些食物留给我们的客人。
EN: Leave some food for our guests.

ZH: 我把这个问题留给你自己思考。
EN: I leave this question for you to think about.

ZH: 我们要留给亲人一些美好的回忆。
EN: We want to leave some good memories for our loved ones.

ZH: 把那个任务留给专业的人做。
EN: Leave that task to the professionals.

ZH: 留给我们一些时间想出一个解决办法。
EN: Give us some time to come up with a solution.

ZH: 请将这份文件留给我看一下。
EN: Please leave this document for me to review.

ZH: 老师让我们把问题给留给下次讨论。
EN: The teacher asked us to leave the question for the next discussion.

ZH: 我把这个惊喜留给了今天的晚餐。
EN: I left this surprise for tonight's dinner.

ZH: 把这个秘密留给自己，不要告诉其他人。
EN: Keep this secret to yourself and don't tell anyone else.

ZH: 留给自己一些时间放松休息。
EN: Leave some time for yourself to relax.

ZH: 他把这个大决定留给了我们来做。
EN: He left this big decision for us to make.

ZH: 老师让我们把这个问题留给课后思考。
EN: The teacher asked us to leave this question for after class to think about.

ZH: 请把这个包裹留给收件人签收。
EN: Please leave this parcel for the recipient to sign.

ZH: 她把这件事留给了最后一刻才处理。
EN: She left this matter to the last minute before dealing with it.

ZH: 留给自己的时间越多，准备就越充分。
EN: The more time you leave for yourself, the more prepared you will be.

ZH: 给孩子留给些自由发展的空间。
EN: Leave some space for children to develop themselves.

ZH: 我们需要把这份工作留给更有经验的人。
EN: We need to leave this job to someone with more experience.
